    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<div dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;" trbidi="on"><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-GzC24Fvx1jQ/Ud8uAlJxNfI/AAAAAAAA4vA/z3fkhj3jABQ/s1600/20130710_171830.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="clear: right; float: right; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 1em;"><img border="0" height="240" src="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-GzC24Fvx1jQ/Ud8uAlJxNfI/AAAAAAAA4vA/z3fkhj3jABQ/s320/20130710_171830.jpg" width="320" /></a></div><br /><a href="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-y6iCV4degCM/Ud8uCupDPTI/AAAAAAAA4vI/xPWqtd2Z_GQ/s1600/20130710_171912.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="clear: right; float: right; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 1em;"><img border="0" height="240" src="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-y6iCV4degCM/Ud8uCupDPTI/AAAAAAAA4vI/xPWqtd2Z_GQ/s320/20130710_171912.jpg" width="320" /></a><br />Two years ago I commented on Sergy's playground with some harsh comments. It seems Sergy was listening and they have updated. A big climbing frame with a wooden chip floor. There are some swings and some springy things.<br /><br />It's &nbsp;a large green space and very quiet. It also has an excellent two lane 100m athletics circle for scooter races.<br /><br />Top tip is to go on Thursday when there is also a take away pizza van on the opposite side of the road.<br /><br />The playground is located behind Sergy's school.</div>

